Text:
@Nanosaur

The file you are looking for is in the game directory. Follow the instructions included in this file. Depending on how you installed the game (the method used) the easiest way is to right click the desktop icon and choose 'open file location'. Look for the bin folder......and there you will see the steam_api.dll. If you installed it with steam look in the steamapps >common >mark_of_the_ninja >bin 

Hope that helps you.
